description:
On a special episode of Everything Iconic, Danny dives into mental health in honor of Mental Health Awareness Month. Danny & his guests talk about their personal struggles w/ depression, anxiety, the tools they use to help get through darkness, & more. 

Crisis Text Line: Text HOME to 741-741 from anywhere in the U.S. *For bonus episodes, join the Patreon at www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic Web: www.EverythingIconic.com Twitter: www.Twitter.com/DannyPellegrino Instagram: www.Instagram.com/DannyPellegrino
